%% Detailed Data Flow: Inventory-Hash-Based Cache Invalidation

sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant E as /parse Endpoint
    participant H as Hash Generator
    participant V as Cache Validator
    participant M as Cache Manager
    participant P as OCR/LLM Processor
    participant X as External APIs

    Note over C,X: Scenario 1: Cache HIT with Valid Inventory

    C->>E: POST /parse<br/>images + inventory
    E->>H: generateInventoryHash(inventory)
    H-->>E: inv_hash: "a1b2c3d4e5f6g7h8"
    E->>H: generateCacheKey(files, inv_hash)
    H-->>E: cache_key: "ocr_xyz...inv_a1b2..."
    E->>M: getCached(cache_key)
    M-->>E: cache_entry {data, inv_hash, cached_at}
    E->>V: validateInventoryHash(entry, current_hash)
    V-->>E: VALID ✓
    E-->>C: 200 OK<br/>{...result, cached: true}

    Note over C,X: Scenario 2: Cache INVALIDATED (Inventory Changed)

    C->>E: POST /parse<br/>images + NEW inventory
    E->>H: generateInventoryHash(new_inventory)
    H-->>E: new_inv_hash: "x9y8z7w6v5u4t3s2"
    E->>H: generateCacheKey(files, new_inv_hash)
    H-->>E: cache_key: "ocr_xyz...inv_x9y8..."
    E->>M: getCached(cache_key)
    M-->>E: cache_entry {data, inv_hash: "a1b2..."}
    E->>V: validateInventoryHash(entry, new_hash)
    V-->>V: Compare: "a1b2..." ≠ "x9y8..."
    V-->>E: INVALID ✗
    E->>M: invalidateCache(cache_key)
    M-->>E: Cache entry deleted
    E->>P: processImages(files)
    P->>X: Google Vision OCR
    X-->>P: ocr_text
    P->>X: Anthropic Claude LLM
    X-->>P: parsed_result
    P-->>E: {extracted, unmapped}
    E->>M: setCachedWithHash(key, result, new_inv_hash, ttl)
    M-->>E: Cached successfully
    E-->>C: 200 OK<br/>{...result, cached: false}

    Note over C,X: Scenario 3: Cache MISS (First Request)

    C->>E: POST /parse<br/>images + inventory
    E->>H: generateInventoryHash(inventory)
    H-->>E: inv_hash: "p0o9i8u7y6t5r4e3"
    E->>H: generateCacheKey(files, inv_hash)
    H-->>E: cache_key: "ocr_abc...inv_p0o9..."
    E->>M: getCached(cache_key)
    M-->>E: null (not found)
    E->>P: processImages(files)
    P->>X: Google Vision OCR
    X-->>P: ocr_text
    P->>X: Anthropic Claude LLM
    X-->>P: parsed_result
    P-->>E: {extracted, unmapped}
    E->>M: setCachedWithHash(key, result, inv_hash, ttl)
    M-->>E: Cached successfully
    E-->>C: 200 OK<br/>{...result, cached: false}

    Note over C,X: Scenario 4: No Inventory Provided (Fallback)

    C->>E: POST /parse<br/>images only (no inventory)
    E->>H: generateSimpleCacheKey(files)
    H-->>E: cache_key: "ocr_def456..."
    E->>M: getCached(cache_key)
    M-->>E: cache_entry {data}
    Note over E,M: No inventory validation
    E-->>C: 200 OK<br/>{...result, cached: true}
